{
	"info": {
		"name": "Django Games API",
		"description": "Collection para a API REST (Django REST Framework + Simple JWT).\n\n**Variáveis:** `baseUrl` (ex.: http://127.0.0.1:8000), `accessToken` (preenchido pelo script de Login JWT).\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT na collection. Endpoints de token não usam Bearer.\n\n**Atenção no projeto:**\n- `app/urls.py` precisa de vírgula após `include('reviews.urls')` e remover `path('')` inválido para o servidor subir.\n- Em `publisher/urls.py` as rotas estão como `platforms/`, igual ao app `platforms` — só a primeira rota é usada. Troque para `publishers/` e use os URLs desta pasta *Publishers*.\n\n**Permissões:** não há `DEFAULT_PERMISSION_CLASSES` nas settings; JWT é opcional salvo se você adicionar permissões nas views.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{accessToken}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000"
		},
		{
			"key": "accessToken",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "refreshToken",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "genreId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "developerId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "platformId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "publisherId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "gameId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "reviewId",
			"value": "1"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth (JWT)",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Obter tokens (login)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const j = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (j.access) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.access);",
									"    if (j.refresh) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refresh);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"seu_usuario\",\n  \"password\": \"sua_senha\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/token/",
						"description": "Simple JWT: retorna `access` e `refresh`. O script salva nas variáveis da collection."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Renovar access token",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const j = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (j.access) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.access);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/token/refresh/"
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Genres",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Listar / Criar",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/genres/"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Criar genre",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"RPG\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/genres/"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Detalhe / Atualizar / Apagar",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/genres/{{genreId}}/"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Atualizar genre (PUT)",
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"RPG Tático\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/genres/{{genreId}}/"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Atualizar parcial (PATCH)",
					"request": {
						"method": "PATCH",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ação\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/genres/{{genreId}}/"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Apagar genre",
					"request": {
						"method": "DELETE",
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/genres/{{genreId}}/"
					}
				}
			]
		},
